name: example-team-repo-main
description: Naming convention: Your repo name should be prefixed by your course cohort (e.g. "COM-FT-DEV2_MAR2024") followed by the surnames of your team members. Create a README file comprising: - a list of all your team members and their roles -  Create a new Project (e.g. Kanban) within the Organisation and link it to your repo - the Project name should be the same as your repo name
